data.description: Don't miss this 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, Great Room, TH floor plan! Located in Joggers Run, with screened in patio overlooking a garden view! Easy living floor plan. First floor has tile throughout with open great room. Stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, & eat-in kitchen. Primary bedroom is located on the 1st floor with laminate wood floors. Good size secondary bedrooms. Newer water heater and a/c unit. Community amenities include , pool tot lot, & basketball court. Great community for all lifestyles and offers a great location close to all the benefits of living in Palm Beach County! Shopping & More. Square Footage is approximate.
